title: Blazin' 5 AFC & NFC Championship Edition

description:
Coming off his 3-1 divisional round picks Colin makes his picks for the AFC and NFC Championship game and RJ Bell of Fox Sports Radio and Pregame.com tells him which way Vegas is leaning on each game in this exclusive podcast.
